Package: MStractor
Type: Package
Title: Workflow functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Luca", family = "Nicolotti",
    email = "luca.nicolotti@awri.com.au",
	role =c("cre","aut"), comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-5910-4010"))
Description: a R workflow developed to streamline pre-processing of metabolomics
    mass spectrometry data. MStractor combines functions for molecular feature
    extraction present in XCMS and CAMERA with user friendly dedicated GUIs.
    It includes chromatographic and MS parameter input, graphical quality control 
    outputs and descriptive statistics calculation.
